features: Roomy Storage Space: The dresser features 7 foldable deep drawers, which provide endless organizational possibilities and protect your privacy as well. The wood top is perfect to place vase, photos, mirror and frequently used items.

Measured 39.4" L x 11.8" W x 30.5" H, the chest of drawers can also be used as TV stand. This media console table is ideal for television up to 45". The fabric bins are great to store CDs, DVDs, game controller, etc.

Sturdy and Durable: Strong steel frame and water-resistant wood top offer stable support and ensure years of use; 4 adjustable feet can protect your floor from scratches and are also designed for uneven ground. Thanks to the handles, the drawers can be opened smoothly.

Multifunction Drawer Organizer: This fabric dresser is ideal for wherever you want to keep clutter under control. Feel free to use it as entertainment center, console table or storage chest in the bedroom, living room, closet, hallway…

Assemble with Ease: The storage drawer unit comes with detailed instructions and all hardware needed for installation, you can easily assemble it in 15-20 minutes without other's help. A installation video guide has been uploaded for help.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 3, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Sturdy and Lightweight Storage Solution in a dresser
reviews.reviewText: I recently added the WLIVE Dresser with 7 Drawers to my bedroom, and it has proven to be an excellent combination of sturdiness and lightweight design. Here's why I find it to be a fantastic storage solution.Impressive Stability:The dresser boasts an impressive level of sturdiness. The materials used in its construction provide a solid foundation, ensuring that it stands securely, even when fully loaded with clothes and belongings. I appreciate the stability, especially considering the often-hefty load dressers carry.Surprisingly Lightweight:What sets this dresser apart is its lightweight design. Despite its sturdy build, the materials used make it surprisingly easy to move around. This feature is a game-changer when rearranging furniture or deciding to give the room a fresh look. It's a dresser that offers stability without sacrificing maneuverability.Easy to Move:The lightweight nature of the dresser makes it incredibly easy to move from one room to another. Whether I'm rearranging furniture or deep cleaning, the dresser doesn't pose any challenges in terms of mobility. The built-in handles on the drawers add to the convenience, allowing for a comfortable grip during transportation.Functional Storage:With seven spacious drawers, this dresser provides ample storage space. Each drawer glides smoothly, and the fabric-lined interior adds a touch of elegance. It's an ideal solution for organizing clothes, accessories, or other personal items in the bedroom, hallway, or entryway.Assembly Made Simple:Putting together the WLIVE Dresser was a straightforward process. The provided instructions were clear, and all the necessary tools were included. The simplicity of assembly adds to the overall positive experience with this furniture piece.In conclusion, the WLIVE Dresser with 7 Drawers has seamlessly integrated into my bedroom, offering a perfect balance of sturdiness and lightweight convenience. If you're looking for a reliable storage solution that's easy to move, this dresser is a fantastic choice.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 15, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Nice casual dresser
reviews.reviewText: Great price for a nice casual, useable, sturdy dresser. Assembly was easy - directions very clear - all parts clearly labeled and organized. So much easier than anything from Ikea. The included multi-tool is appreciated, but if you use your own tools (especially a small screwdriver) it can be assembled much faster. Took me about 45 minutes.We are very pleased with the look and quality.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 6, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Great dresser for a child
reviews.reviewText: I bought the 7 drawer dresser for my 4 year old's room and it seems like it will work perfectly. It was very simple to put together, instructions included detailed pictures and worded descriptions. Although it is slimmer than I imagined, there's plenty of room for all his clothes. I also like the look and sturdiness of the fabric drawers, they are not as flimsy as other fabric drawers I've bought in the past.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 3, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Ease of assembly, not sure on durability of product.
reviews.reviewText: The media could not be loaded. Pros: It only took me about 15 minutes to assemble, very clear instructions. All holes were in right places. It looks very cute and fits the space I needed it in. Not heavy, just what I needed.Cons: some of the fabric cover of the drawers came already to the point of ripping, especially on the left side of drawers, looking at dresser(see photos). I wish there was a way to get replacement drawers, as I am not going thru the dissasembling process to return it. This took a couple of stars of rating as it has dubious durability now.I will review again after I contact seller about this issue.

reviews.reviewText: I purchased 4 of these dressers for my bedroom. I have doubled my storage space.I actually used 2 for nightstands. Perfect height for my lamps. They look great. This product is exceptional. I am 76 and I put each dresser together in 30 minutes.They are packaged very well!
